Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,860)\fs80}{\bord4\shad4\blur1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H585A59&\4c&H000000&\4a&HB4&}吉祥寺 武藏野女子高中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对于大家就算假日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还是答应了这次突然的邀约
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我深表感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天特别找大家来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是有一件事想和大家商量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,商量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,超郑重的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉一定有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,前一阵子我们武藏野女子高中Jet Race社
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,受到关东Jet Race协会的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,希望我们帮忙制作宣传影片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为想让更多年轻世代参与成为选手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,需要投入清新的创意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以来麻烦我们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是要我们一起帮忙吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不 影片已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也提交给协会了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但似乎是和协会要求的内容有些落差…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,被退回来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,太悲伤又太难过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,害我肚子饿到受不了了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,辉夜小姐和黑丸好可怜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,明明做好了对方却不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,的确会很难过吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,难道紫集院小姐要和我们商量的事情是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,既然头都已经洗下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就要好好把它完成才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为了要做出可以让协会接受的宣传影片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,希望可以借重各位的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是严重到会被退回的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们到底是做了怎样的宣传影片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 连标准都不知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,根本谈不上怎么帮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,知彼之前要先知己嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,黑丸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,打开 好想吃焦糖布丁的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是机关耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh  what's happened
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet Race是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,驾驶者和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,射击者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,两人一组
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,驰骋于水面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,热血的水上运动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,表面看似华丽的Jet Race
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但其实当中需要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,每天持续不懈怠的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻人们 一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,把你们的青春奉献给Jet Race吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,才不会有人看了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,会想去尝试Jet Race啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们认真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这超烂的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就算本来有点兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看了这个以后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我觉得还不错啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,宣传影片做成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是笨蛋吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,傻眼猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然锻炼的确很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这好像有点太超过了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太Crazy了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是敢说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们来拍的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,会怎么做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我来我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,宣传影片的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就交给Hell's Kitchen吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是子瑜氏和媞娜氏来拍的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那一定是全宇宙都会想看的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事就交给你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们到底会做出怎样的成品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你就好好期待然后等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是用粘答答鲜奶油装饰的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,甜点天使 子瑜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只有甜蜜的话就大无趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我是薄荷小恶魔媞娜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人加起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是「Hell's Kitchen」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,果然好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,已经够了啦 快点开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊 一般来说都会超开心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好了啦 子瑜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这边就用工作模式应付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就请观赏我们制作的宣传影片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这个怎么看都是偶像的宣传影片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,跟Jet Race相辟的要素也太少了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是Hell's Kitchen超可爱的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是…子瑜和媞娜的魅力都被好好的表达出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外没有了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这就单纯是Hell's Kitchen的宣传影片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这样看来是要我们出马了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,应该说 要拍影片的话 当然要靠我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我和柚子两个人 来帮你们拍出超厉害的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要拜托大家也一起帮忙啰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以好好宣传Jet Race的话 是可以啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好 这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就快点来开拍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好普通喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,都帮忙了 你们那什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我说啊 应该像这样 你看 多一点像这样啊 那样之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…像那样的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,应该说要拍一般看不太到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是Jet Race当中会做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,超爱你的啦 柚子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,来拍保养Orcano的画面怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那太不起眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我觉得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet Race常被认为重要的只是驾驶者和射击者的搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,和机体的搭配也是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,驾驶人员有多理解机体的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 总之就是清洗Orcano对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,先不论机体的保养
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有什么必要穿成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是加利福尼亚流的洗法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们来教你们怎么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,机体是很纤细的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要很温柔的对待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,透过肌肤相亲来提升对机体的掌握度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也要…跟著做吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说什么都愿意帮忙的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我没说过什么都帮吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在考验小凛和小美沙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对Orcano的爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小美沙 我们加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧 美沙美沙也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 很好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对对对 再多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下镜头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这边再用力一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:12:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,此等美景 我就收下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,给我差不多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 这次又要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,凛凛 就是那个啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,柚子我超爱你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这种宣传啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也是要拍一点这样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,柚子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,动感不够啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,脚麻掉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,被这样做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的 这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是神轿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…真夏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也是Cool Japan的一部分吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,凛凛你很懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿呦 嘿呦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet呀嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿呦 嘿呦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet呀嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿呦 嘿呦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet呀嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿呦 嘿呦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Jet呀嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这种摇晃 好像Jet乘在浪上的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,轻抚在脸上的风…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像…就好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿呦 嘿呦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这群家伙 给我多用点力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是在小看人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了你们啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真亏你们能到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,做为奖赏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就由我亲自来当你们的对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,邪恶女皇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,辉夜奴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我非得做这种事不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那两个人说想试看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,女仆女仆女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,往南方的小岛出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,去寻找双胞胎美少女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,胜利的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就在她们两人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这座岛的守护神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有听说是美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但没想到这么幼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为至少会有这么大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,气死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过是一堆脂肪的聚集体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好嚣张的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好像还是不够
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,冲击力不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是要用那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我们穿成这样一字排开…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们到底打算做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还用说吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,说到Jet Race当然是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,浴室没人啰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,柚子你也去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚收到协会的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,说因为宣传影片 要大约一个礼拜的审查时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以请提前一周交…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为要花时间检查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以叫我们一定要早一周交啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话 截稿日不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明天正午前…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有要求一定要遵守时间 就算迟一分钟也不会收件的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙根本什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这之后还要加装饰特效啊 或上字幕之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很多事情要做好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,总之影片档在我们这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也只能剪剪贴贴一下交了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,完成…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,之后只要送出就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,又怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚认真看了一下邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,上面说东西要直接交给媒体部门才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,柚子 我快要看不懂日文了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只能烧成光碟拿过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,现在搭电车过去也来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H434343&\frz16.21\pos(1266,1026)}宣传影片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frx0\fry5\fax0.37\frz347\move(1826,439.333,-44,400,0,3388)}关东Jet Race协会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,赶上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的 这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那么来说明关于Jet Race的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 Jet君你可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧 Raee
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 Jet Race是两人一组的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,驾驶者和那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,射击者啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 对吼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你们提交给协会的宣传影片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好像出了点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以协会紧急把自己制作的这版
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,当做正式版本播出了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们的努力到底算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,明明那么拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我也很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是忍耐着帮忙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,多么残酷的结果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我已经够羞耻的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,添上更多耻辱了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 我觉得还不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Race也满可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,重点不在那里啦 小美沙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要遵守规则 才能快乐的享受Jet Race喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,和Race约好了喔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,===============ED===============
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:45.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,为了达成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,儿时的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:51.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,而来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:56.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,虽然总是感到烦恼和挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:58.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,但现在先把这些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:02.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,都放到一旁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:08.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,看啊看啊看啊 已经抑制不住的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:13.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,但是但是但是 我还可以这般奔驰吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:17.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,可以的 两个人一起的话就可以做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,比风更快 比风更远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:25.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,不管哪里都能去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,我们将从波浪的间隙中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:32.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,拔尖而出 向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:39.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,往境界线的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,===============ED===============
